	<p>This book is written for developers who have previous experience with <strong>PHP</strong> and <strong>PHP frameworks</strong>, such as <strong>Zend</strong> or <strong>CakePHP</strong>, and want to start developing and working with <strong>Magento</strong>. Even developers with previous experience with <strong>Magento</strong> will find the book extremely useful to gain a full understanding of <strong>Magento</strong> fundamentals, architecture, and overall philosophy.</p>

